Package com.github.valid8j.pcond.forms Description

This package stores entry-point classes to static import for your conveniences.

Functions

Methods that return printable functions are provided by this class.

Predicates

Methods that return printable predicates are provided by this class.

Printables

Methods to create printable functions and predicates are provided by this class.
